metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Si Ya No Estas Conmigo is significantly more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Si Ya No Estas Conmigo has sections analyzed in the following keys: A Minor,  and C Mixolydian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: Another thing I love 'bout Kany is that she also uses borrowed chords to create hard-to-guess scales. But I guess this is C Melodic Major aka C Mixolydian b6.
